# JobFlow Frontend ğŸ¨

This is the **React frontend** for the JobFlow job application tracker.

Built with:

- React (Vite)
- React Router
- Custom CSS (glassmorphism + animated background)
- Fetch API to call the Node.js backend

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Beautiful animated login page (liquid / wave background, glass UI)
- Login & JWT token storage in `localStorage`
- Protected dashboard route
- Fetches job applications from backend
- Ready to extend with:
  - Register page
  - Add / Edit job forms
  - Job filters & stats

---

## ğŸ›  Tech Stack

- **React** (Vite)
- **React Router DOM**
- **Plain CSS** for custom UI
- **Fetch API** to call backend

